Ranger Help for: winter's bite
================================

SYNTAX:      winterbite <target> or wbite <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   8
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  religious

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to channel the fury of winter into a cold
damage attack against a target. The biting cold saps the strength of
the enemy. Winter's Bite is more effective in arctic and cold terrains
and during the winter season, when the power of frost is at its peak.
The damage dealt depends on the Ranger's wisdom, guild level, and
the current terrain and season.
